ddf.catalog.filter.impl

Class SimpleFilterDelegate<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ddf.catalog.filter.FilterDelegate<T>
      • ddf.catalog.filter.impl.SimpleFilterDelegate<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Generic type that the FilterDelegate will return as a final result
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContentTypeFilterDelegate, QueryTypeFilterDelegate, RestFilterDelegate, TagsFilterDelegate, ValidationQueryDelegate, WfsFilterDelegate, WfsFilterDelegate, WktExtractionFilterDelegate

    public abstract class SimpleFilterDelegate<T>
extends FilterDelegate<T>
    Implements a simplified version of the FilterDelegate where every method rolls up a to higher abstracted method
